nappropriate, not illegal and therefore, then this is the leap that you\u0027re making here whether you\u0027re saying it or not, therefore, it\u0027s likely he molested a seven-year old.","docId":"140203pmt","qSentId":437,"aSentId":438},{"question":"Have you ever been attracted to an 18-year-old woman?","answer":"Michael, I\u0027m in a bizarre -- Michael, I\u0027m in this composition of...","docId":"140203pmt","qSentId":491,"aSentId":492},{"question":"Have you ever been?","answer":"... having to jump in an answer a question on my own show.","docId":"140203pmt","qSentId":493,"aSentId":494},{"question":"... who knows?","answer":"Some would say a lot of...","docId":"140203pmt","qSentId":503,"aSentId":504},{"question":"But what I was saying is because you don\u0027t know that it didn\u0027t happen either, do you, in the same position as me?","answer":"You know, Piers, I don\u0027t know that you haven\u0027t molested someone.","docId":"140203pmt","qSentId":525,"aSentId":526},{"question":"What should we make of this?","answer":"LOOM: Well, first of all, I\u0027ve never met anybody in this case.","docId":"140203pmt","qSentId":543,"aSentId":544}]